sps\", \"from\": 625, \"to\": 630}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Every now and then, concerts kicked off beside the halfpipe and fans danced in bibs and beanies.\", \"from\": 659, \"to\": 755, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"concerts\", \"from\": 679, \"to\": 687}, {\"ngram\": \"the halfpipe\", \"from\": 706, \"to\": 718}, {\"ngram\": \"fans\", \"from\": 723, \"to\": 727}, {\"ngram\": \"bibs\", \"from\": 738, \"to\": 742}, {\"ngram\": \"beanies\", \"from\": 747, \"to\": 754}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Welcome to The Snow League, the brainchild of Olympic legendShaun White.\", \"from\": 756, \"to\": 828, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Snow League\", \"from\": 767, \"to\": 782}, {\"ngram\": \"the brainchild\", \"from\": 784, \"to\": 798}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic legendShaun White\", \"from\": 802, \"to\": 827}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Snow League claims to be 'the future of winter sports competition,' the first professional league dedicated to snowboarding and freeskiing, where 'the next generation of superstars' compete for a season purse of $2.2million.\", \"from\": 830, \"to\": 1058, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Snow League\", \"from\": 830, \"to\": 845}, {\"ngram\": \"the future\", \"from\": 860, \"to\": 870}, {\"ngram\": \"winter sports competition\", \"from\": 874, \"to\": 899}, {\"ngram\": \"snowboarding\", \"from\": 945, \"to\": 957}, {\"ngram\": \"freeskiing\", \"from\": 962, \"to\": 972}, {\"ngram\": \"the next generation\", \"from\": 981, \"to\": 1000}, {\"ngram\": \"superstars\", \"from\": 1004, \"to\": 1014}, {\"ngram\": \"a season purse\", \"from\": 1028, \"to\": 1042}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Last month, the Daily Mail travelled to Aspen to witness the action from the edge of the halfpipe, from down on the snow and up in the VIP lounge, where White watched the latest creation of a remarkable career.\", \"from\": 1060, \"to\": 1270, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1076, \"end\": 1086, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org